<div class="lg:text-center">
  <h2 class="text-base text-brand font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">For Developers</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Spend more time building and less time project planning</p>
  <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl text-gray-500 lg:mx-auto">Showcase allows you to find user submitted project ideas to complete, get feedback, and flex your developer muscles.</p>
</div>

